review: Dr Raka Guleria madam is a very experience lady. She is very nice and friendly while dealing with her patients. She gave me right counseling and taking treatment from her.

I have taken appointment for my sister-in-law for covid and consultation was book. Doctor was quite good and consultation was done on time, after the consultation treatment has been provided and completely satisfied by this doctor. We came to know about this doctor from one-off our family members and I would like to recommend this doctor for my friends and family members also.
